snippet.title: スキップ・ビート！　ゲームOP　Skip Beat PS2 Game OP
snippet.description: Skip Beat PS2 Game :D  Due out May 28th I believe.  It's beautiful.  I am so happy to see Reino and SmilySpiky!  I originally labeled it as a PV but this is the OP according to the website.
